bio: As of 2014 Adrian Metzner is working as a software developer. His focus lies in IT Security as well as DevOps. At WPS - Workplace Solutions he is working as a Software-Architect, IT Security Consultant and Trainer for the iSAQB Modules Cloud-Infra and WEBSEC.
